You see, if I work out
the strategy right...

746
01:01:44,800 --> 01:01:47,200
you gotta hold up
your end now.

747
01:01:47,300 --> 01:01:48,800
- You know?
- I know.

748
01:01:51,600 --> 01:01:54,800
How much is this?
Donnie, you got some thing on you?

749
01:01:54,600 --> 01:01:56,900
- What are you doing there?
- How about five dollars?

750
01:01:59,900 --> 01:02:03,400
- You're doing an amazing job.
