forget about it.

765
01:03:03,900 --> 01:03:07,600
All right. Thank you very much.
I got it.

766
01:03:07,600 --> 01:03:11,600
Let me tell you something.
I don't get this boat for Lefty--

767
01:03:11,600 --> 01:03:13,700
- Forget about it?
